  .codepen(data-height="200" data-editable="true" data-theme-id="0" data-slug-hash="rqGLyq" data-default-tab="css,result" data-user="htmlboy")

%section
  %pre
    %code.css
      :preserve
        h1, h2, h3 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }
  %p
    Selectors can be grouped with commas in order to assign them the same&nbsp;styles.

%section
  %pre
    %code.css
      h1 {font-size: 24px;}
      h1 {font-size: 20px;}
  %p
    In case of two statements in conflict (same selector, same property),
    the statement below&nbsp;prevails.

